{"word":"μεριμνάω","slug":"μεριμνάω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>μεριμνάω</el></b> [<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ cp.\">cp.</a> the <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ prec.\">prec.</a> back-formation <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:μέριμνα\">μέριμνα</a></el>] ‘be uneasy in mind or spirit’<b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> focus on worrying about meeting one’s needs <b>be anxious/concerned (about) <a href='B:470 6:25'>Mt 6:25</a>, <a href='B:470 6:27'>27f</a>, 31, 34; <a href='B:470 10:19'>10:19</a>; <a href='B:490 10:41'>Lk 10: 41</a>; <a href='B:490 12:11'>12:11</a>, <a href='B:490 12:22'>22</a>, <a href='B:490 12:25'>25</a>, <a href='B:490 12:26'>26</a>; <a href='B:570 4:6'>Phil 4:6</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> focus on the need or interest of another <b>be solicitous (about/for), look out for <a href='B:530 7:32-34'>1 Cor 7:32-34</a>; <a href='B:530 12:25'>12:25</a>; <a href='B:570 2:20'>Phil 2:20</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:μέριμνα\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:μερίς\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}